1
00:01:02,520 --> 00:01:04,239
I'm not opposed to becoming Emperor.

2
00:01:04,879 --> 00:01:07,200
But Mother must have told you about Yuji.

3
00:01:08,760 --> 00:01:09,719
I still have patients to see.

4
00:01:09,840 --> 00:01:11,079
I need to get back to work.

5
00:01:11,799 --> 00:01:12,560
Yuji.

6
00:01:13,840 --> 00:01:14,879
Who's Yuji?

7
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:20,319
Princess Ouyang has arrived, hasn't she?

8
00:01:21,439 --> 00:01:22,439
You know me?

9
00:01:34,319 --> 00:01:35,879
Mother warns me every day,

10
00:01:38,079 --> 00:01:40,280
saying once the Prince becomes Emperor,

11
00:01:42,239 --> 00:01:43,719
he'll naturally abandon me

12
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:46,040
to marry the princess of the State of Yan.

13
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:48,120
You seem rather pitiful.

14
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:51,040
I won't let the Prince abandon you.

15
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:55,319
But I need to make some things clear.

16
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:57,519
I'll be the Empress,

17
00:01:57,879 --> 00:02:00,280
and you'll only get to be a Noble Consort.

18
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:02,319
But rest assured,

19
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:05,680
I have zero interest in your Prince.

20
00:02:05,879 --> 00:02:07,439
You two can stay just as in love.

21
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:11,759
Thank you for your kindness, Princess,

22
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,639
but I don't have many days left.

23
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:18,479
You needn't worry at all.

24
00:02:22,039 --> 00:02:23,039
You...

25
00:02:23,479 --> 00:02:25,879
Are you really that sick?

26
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:27,759
There.

27
00:02:27,759 --> 00:02:28,639
You'll be fine now.

28
00:02:28,639 --> 00:02:29,840
Just take your medicine on time.

29
00:02:35,919 --> 00:02:37,319
You two still refuse to leave?

30
00:02:38,159 --> 00:02:39,879
Yuji's illness isn't cured yet.

31
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:42,280
I will absolutely never leave her.

32
00:02:42,639 --> 00:02:44,080
It's not that we don't want to leave.

33
00:02:44,319 --> 00:02:46,479
The whole nation is waiting for you.

34
00:02:46,479 --> 00:02:48,039
My heart belongs only to Yuji.

35
00:02:49,039 --> 00:02:50,599
Everything else, to me,

36
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:53,039
is nothing but a passing cloud.

37
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,719
Look, my Prince,

38
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:58,520
Being Emperor and saving Yuji don't clash.

39
00:02:58,919 --> 00:02:59,800
Think about it.

40
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,159
Once you become Emperor,

41
00:03:01,159 --> 00:03:02,879
the palace has so many imperial physicians

42
00:03:03,039 --> 00:03:04,680
who can quickly cure Yuji.

43
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,919
Yuji can't be cured by ordinary doctors.

44
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,919
Else I wouldn't have spent years studying

45
00:03:09,919 --> 00:03:10,840
and searching through every case file,

46
00:03:11,319 --> 00:03:14,960
to find someone with her exact illness.

47
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,039
My Prince,

48
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:21,240
may I be so bold as to ask,

49
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:24,240
what illness does Yuji have?

50
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:32,639
Does it hurt?

51
00:03:33,879 --> 00:03:34,960
Excruciatingly so.

52
00:03:36,439 --> 00:03:38,080
Then how do you bear it?

53
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:42,240
Compared to parting with the Prince,

54
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:44,919
this is nothing.

55
00:03:48,280 --> 00:03:49,080
Princess,

56
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:49,840
Hmm?

57
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:53,039
Have you ever loved anyone?

58
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:54,919
Me?

59
00:03:59,479 --> 00:04:00,840
So you have, then.

60
00:04:04,879 --> 00:04:06,240
If you love someone,

61
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:14,080
you wouldn't want the pain of losing them.

62
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:21,439
Actually, love isn't everything.

63
00:04:23,519 --> 00:04:24,639
What you just said...

64
00:04:25,959 --> 00:04:27,279
that love isn't everything,

65
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:34,720
I don't think that's what you truly mean.

66
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:41,720
Are they red rashes like mine?

67
00:04:50,279 --> 00:04:51,160
Forgive my bluntness,

68
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,639
but I can't cure your illness.

69
00:04:57,279 --> 00:04:59,079
Special Envoy Qi, someone beat you up, didn't they?

70
00:05:01,839 --> 00:05:03,040
Oh.

71
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:04,800
This, well...

72
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:06,560
Along the way,

73
00:05:07,639 --> 00:05:09,120
I suffered a bit of violent abuse.

74
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:11,160
I won't keep you two any longer.

75
00:05:11,639 --> 00:05:13,240
I still have many things to attend to.

76
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:14,079
Hey.

77
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:17,279
My Prince, won't you reconsider?

78
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:20,439
Even if I become Emperor,

79
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:23,839
I'd never let Princess Ouyang be Empress.

80
00:05:24,759 --> 00:05:25,560
Special Envoy Qi,

81
00:05:26,439 --> 00:05:27,519
would you be willing?

82
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:34,560
Special Envoy Qi and I are kindred spirits.

83
00:05:35,519 --> 00:05:36,439
After you.

84
00:05:41,079 --> 00:05:43,240
Prince Chu refuses to be Emperor.

85
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:44,959
Who says I mind?

86
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:45,879
Well, that works out.

87
00:05:45,879 --> 00:05:47,240
This Prince...

88
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:48,680
This princess doesn't want to marry him either.

89
00:05:49,040 --> 00:05:49,759
Let's go.

90
00:05:49,759 --> 00:05:50,839
On to the next one.

91
00:05:58,040 --> 00:05:59,680
We've pretty much exhausted our options.

92
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,240
If this keeps up,

93
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:03,240
we'll have to let Liu Heng be Emperor.

94
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:04,680
You've got some nerve saying that.

95
00:06:05,079 --> 00:06:08,040
Who started this whole mess?

96
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:22,639
You are...

97
00:06:22,639 --> 00:06:23,920
Princess Ouyang.

98
00:06:24,839 --> 00:06:26,360
The medicine to cure Yuji,

99
00:06:26,519 --> 00:06:27,959
when will you finish developing it?

100
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,560
Princess, you put me in a tough spot.

101
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:35,439
I want to find that cure more than anyone.

102
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:38,480
Fine.

103
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:41,839
I've decided you'll be my Emperor.

104
00:06:43,079 --> 00:06:44,680
We'll be staying here with you.

105
00:06:45,079 --> 00:06:47,079
Once you find the cure for Yuji,

106
00:06:47,519 --> 00:06:48,480
we'll return to the capital.

107
00:06:49,639 --> 00:06:51,240
Even if I don't make you Empress?

108
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:55,839
Yes.

109
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:17,040
Have you found the cure yet?

110
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:19,839
However many patients you need,

111
00:07:19,839 --> 00:07:21,040
I'll round them up for you.

112
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:26,480
What are you doing?

113
00:07:27,439 --> 00:07:29,519
Are you crazy? What are you doing?

114
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:30,839
Hey, what are you up to?

115
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:29,680
Hey.

116
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:53,879
It's been so long now.

117
00:08:54,639 --> 00:08:56,480
How much longer do you plan to hold on?

118
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:02,840
If the Dowager Consort wants me to die sooner,

119
00:09:05,279 --> 00:09:06,720
just pay me more.

120
00:09:08,919 --> 00:09:10,879
As long as you leave my son,

121
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,720
I'll give you whatever you ask.

122
00:09:13,279 --> 00:09:14,320
Name your price.

123
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:16,679
Two hundred thousand taels.

124
00:09:16,679 --> 00:09:18,759
Not a coin less, or I'm not leaving.

125
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:20,080
You...

126
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:22,519
My, aren't you greedy.

127
00:09:22,919 --> 00:09:26,399
You might not live to spend this money.

128
00:09:28,559 --> 00:09:29,360
Shh.

129
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:35,360
By rights, with my poison in you,

130
00:09:35,879 --> 00:09:37,240
you should've been dead long ago.

131
00:09:39,519 --> 00:09:41,240
Yet here you are, still hanging on,

132
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:45,320
trying to ruin my plans.

133
00:09:47,279 --> 00:09:49,039
The Prince loves me so deeply.

134
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:52,720
How could I bear to die?

135
00:09:54,919 --> 00:09:56,360
If the Dowager Consort refuses,

136
00:09:58,480 --> 00:09:59,919
I'll just take the antidote

137
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:03,919
and run off with the Prince.

138
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:04,759
You...

139
00:10:10,559 --> 00:10:12,320
Fine.

140
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:15,480
You really value money over your own life.

141
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:18,240
Yuji is in league with the Dowager Consort!

142
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:18,480
Shh.

143
00:10:18,559 --> 00:10:19,360
No.

144
00:10:21,159 --> 00:10:22,519
You can't tell Prince Chu.

145
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:23,879
Hm?

146
00:10:25,039 --> 00:10:25,960
Why not?

147
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:27,919
Just do as I say.

148
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:32,639
What...

149
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:36,080
Why's she been acting so strange lately?

150
00:10:57,120 --> 00:10:57,919
My Prince,

151
00:10:59,039 --> 00:11:00,360
your Yu is too weak.

152
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:02,840
I can't hold on any longer.

153
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:07,240
I don't want you to see me die like this.

154
00:11:08,919 --> 00:11:12,480
I hope we can be married in the next life.

155
00:11:14,039 --> 00:11:15,279
My beloved Yuji.

156
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:28,720
My Prince,

157
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:29,879
a patient is here to see you.

158
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:37,639
Leave me.

159
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:41,120
I won't be treating anyone anymore.

160
00:11:48,919 --> 00:11:51,519
I hope after you marry my son,

161
00:11:51,919 --> 00:11:53,759
you won't be like that Yuji,

162
00:11:53,759 --> 00:11:54,919
clinging to him every single day.

163
00:11:55,919 --> 00:11:56,840
Don't worry.

164
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:58,559
I don't like Prince Chu at all.

165
00:11:59,159 --> 00:12:01,720
I only hope to be his wife in name only,

166
00:12:01,759 --> 00:12:03,120
each living our own lives.

167
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:07,559
You're exactly the daughter-in-law I want.

168
00:12:08,519 --> 00:12:10,679
Making it worth getting rid of that wench.

169
00:12:12,679 --> 00:12:14,720
Yuji only brought it on herself.

170
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:18,360
You just obliged her, Dowager Consort.

171
00:12:19,919 --> 00:12:21,639
You really are the sensible one.

172
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:28,720
I wonder if Yuji really did die,

173
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:33,039
or if she snuck off to find the antidote.

174
00:12:35,639 --> 00:12:37,240
How could she possibly have an antidote?

175
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:40,240
Since you're being so good,

176
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:42,080
I won't hide it from you.

177
00:12:43,039 --> 00:12:46,240
It needs a thousand-year-old Suoluozi.

178
00:12:46,679 --> 00:12:48,519
Even I don't have one yet.

179
00:12:49,639 --> 00:12:51,679
Then...

180
00:12:51,879 --> 00:12:55,080
They say the last one in Chu City

181
00:12:55,080 --> 00:12:57,559
was taken by the bandits on this mountain.

182
00:12:58,039 --> 00:13:00,519
How could it ever end up in Yuji's hands?

183
00:13:01,480 --> 00:13:04,480
Hahaha!

184
00:13:19,039 --> 00:13:20,879
When did you team up with the Dowager Consort?

185
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:22,039
Huh?

186
00:13:22,879 --> 00:13:23,679
Uh...

187
00:13:25,360 --> 00:13:26,480
You heard everything.

188
00:13:28,120 --> 00:13:28,720
Actually...

189
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:30,759
Why have you been acting so differently?

190
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:35,879
Since I promised you

191
00:13:36,039 --> 00:13:37,879
to find you a match and make you Empress,

192
00:13:38,120 --> 00:13:39,240
I won't let you down.

193
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:41,399
Why are you pressuring Prince Chu so hard?

194
00:13:42,399 --> 00:13:43,039
I...

195
00:13:45,960 --> 00:13:47,440
I've just got my eye on Prince Chu.

196
00:13:51,240 --> 00:13:52,039
Fine.

197
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:55,840
Since you want to stay here

198
00:13:55,879 --> 00:13:58,679
and force Prince Chu to rule, I won't stop you.

199
00:13:59,679 --> 00:14:01,360
Then the Crown Prince and I will be leaving.

200
00:14:16,440 --> 00:14:17,240
Dowager Consort.

201
00:14:17,840 --> 00:14:19,720
The Crown Prince and I must be on our way.

202
00:14:19,720 --> 00:14:21,039
We've come to bid you farewell.

203
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:23,919
There's no rush, is there?

204
00:14:24,440 --> 00:14:26,240
You must have a farewell drink.

205
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:28,279
A farewell drink?

206
00:14:29,559 --> 00:14:30,360
My apologies.

207
00:14:30,879 --> 00:14:32,519
Prince Chu has just lost his beloved wife.

208
00:14:32,759 --> 00:14:35,679
He likely can't return to rule with us.

209
00:14:35,840 --> 00:14:38,360
I hope the Dowager Consort understands.

210
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:45,120
Do you all think I'm heartless?

211
00:14:45,879 --> 00:14:46,679
Yes.

212
00:14:48,039 --> 00:14:49,320
No, no, not at all.

213
00:14:49,320 --> 00:14:50,360
Please don't misunderstand.

214
00:14:53,759 --> 00:14:55,159
I'm just...

215
00:14:55,759 --> 00:14:59,240
a mother with high hopes for her son.

216
00:15:01,679 --> 00:15:03,840
Since he doesn't want to be Emperor,

217
00:15:04,639 --> 00:15:06,559
I won't force him anymore.

218
00:15:08,279 --> 00:15:09,080
Come.

219
00:15:09,919 --> 00:15:11,039
Bottoms up!

220
00:15:11,360 --> 00:15:13,080
I'll see you out of the city.

221
00:15:28,320 --> 00:15:29,360
Thank you, Dowager Consort.

222
00:15:44,240 --> 00:15:45,240
Hahaha!

223
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:48,840
Go keep that little wench company.

224
00:15:49,039 --> 00:15:50,320
Guards!

225
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:51,120
Yes!

226
00:15:52,759 --> 00:15:53,720
Hey!

227
00:15:56,240 --> 00:15:57,120
Let go of me!

228
00:16:00,759 --> 00:16:02,320
Crown Prince, I really give up on you.

229
00:16:02,440 --> 00:16:03,480
Ever since I became your Special Envoy,

230
00:16:03,480 --> 00:16:05,679
I've been locked up more than I've cooked.

231
00:16:06,320 --> 00:16:08,159
I haven't been to jail many times before.

232
00:16:08,279 --> 00:16:09,240
It's quite a novelty.

233
00:16:09,720 --> 00:16:10,279
Hey!

234
00:16:10,279 --> 00:16:10,879
Yuji!

235
00:16:11,720 --> 00:16:12,639
You're not dead!

236
00:16:12,679 --> 00:16:13,559
There's someone else here?

237
00:16:16,960 --> 00:16:18,679
The Dowager Consort can't bear bloodshed.

238
00:16:19,919 --> 00:16:21,519
Since I'm sick anyway,

239
00:16:22,279 --> 00:16:24,159
she left me here to fend for myself.

240
00:16:24,240 --> 00:16:24,840
Oh, by the way,

241
00:16:24,840 --> 00:16:27,039
I overheard you by the wall that day.

242
00:16:27,039 --> 00:16:28,120
Don't you have an antidote?

243
00:16:28,120 --> 00:16:28,919
Bring it out and use it!

244
00:16:31,559 --> 00:16:33,240
That was just a lie I told the Dowager Consort.

245
00:16:33,240 --> 00:16:33,519
Huh?

246
00:16:33,519 --> 00:16:34,120
What?

247
00:16:34,120 --> 00:16:35,879
How could I possibly have an antidote?

248
00:16:38,480 --> 00:16:41,159
The Prince's care alone has kept me alive.

249
00:16:43,279 --> 00:16:44,759
I'm going to die sooner or later.

250
00:16:46,360 --> 00:16:48,759
The Dowager Consort controls our finances.

251
00:16:49,679 --> 00:16:51,879
I just wanted to help the Prince earn some money,

252
00:16:52,960 --> 00:16:54,519
to help him escape the Dowager Consort.

253
00:16:55,279 --> 00:16:56,480
It's been so hard.

254
00:16:56,679 --> 00:16:58,159
Yuji, you've truly gone to great lengths.

255
00:16:58,320 --> 00:17:00,639
But the current situation looks grim.

256
00:17:01,240 --> 00:17:03,519
The Dowager Consort must have the Late Emperor's Jade Pendant,

257
00:17:03,559 --> 00:17:04,680
and forced the Prince into the palace.

258
00:17:04,680 --> 00:17:07,200
The Dowager Consort ordered all patients to leave.

259
00:17:10,920 --> 00:17:12,079
I'm free!

260
00:17:12,480 --> 00:17:13,680
I'm free!

261
00:17:31,880 --> 00:17:33,839
You're about to become Emperor.

262
00:17:33,920 --> 00:17:34,960
Mind your manners.

263
00:17:38,880 --> 00:17:39,440
Hey.

264
00:17:39,440 --> 00:17:40,039
Oh, right.

265
00:17:40,279 --> 00:17:41,720
Ouyang Yan will come to save us.

266
00:17:41,880 --> 00:17:42,960
Her martial arts are so impressive.

267
00:17:43,079 --> 00:17:44,359
Those guys outside are weaklings.

268
00:17:44,839 --> 00:17:46,039
She can take them down easily.

269
00:17:46,359 --> 00:17:47,680
Everyone has different pursuits.

270
00:17:47,680 --> 00:17:48,480
For her...

271
00:17:50,480 --> 00:17:51,839
Tell your boss to come see me.

272
00:17:51,880 --> 00:17:53,240
Who dared to hurt my brothers?

273
00:17:54,240 --> 00:17:55,039
Move.

274
00:17:59,640 --> 00:18:01,359
You're the one who hurt my brothers.

275
00:18:02,079 --> 00:18:02,880
Cut the nonsense.

276
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:07,880
Lady Hero.

277
00:18:07,880 --> 00:18:09,440
Times are tough these days.

278
00:18:09,519 --> 00:18:10,200
I beg you, Lady Hero,

279
00:18:10,200 --> 00:18:12,240
please spare my brothers.

280
00:18:12,359 --> 00:18:13,640
Please let us off.

281
00:18:13,640 --> 00:18:14,680
You won't fight me?

282
00:18:15,640 --> 00:18:16,480
No, I won't.

283
00:18:16,480 --> 00:18:18,720
Bullying a young girl when she's down,

284
00:18:18,880 --> 00:18:19,880
if word got out about something like that,

285
00:18:19,880 --> 00:18:20,920
how could I show my face anymore?

286
00:18:21,440 --> 00:18:21,920
How about this:

287
00:18:21,920 --> 00:18:23,279
whatever you fancy on my mountain,

288
00:18:23,680 --> 00:18:24,839
just take it.

289
00:18:26,640 --> 00:18:27,599
No offense, then.

290
00:18:27,599 --> 00:18:29,440
You have a Suoluozi plant.

291
00:18:29,480 --> 00:18:30,000
Hand it over

292
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:31,079
and I'll leave the mountain at once.

293
00:18:32,039 --> 00:18:33,839
Ouyang Yan values loyalty.

294
00:18:34,759 --> 00:18:35,839
I can tell.

295
00:18:36,279 --> 00:18:37,480
She'll come to save you.

296
00:18:40,839 --> 00:18:41,680
Hey.

297
00:18:41,680 --> 00:18:42,319
Zhenzhen.

298
00:18:42,559 --> 00:18:43,480
Crown Prince.

299
00:18:43,480 --> 00:18:44,440
You came to save us!

300
00:18:44,440 --> 00:18:45,119
No, no, not really.

301
00:18:45,119 --> 00:18:46,680
I was gathering material for my novel,

302
00:18:46,720 --> 00:18:48,839
to learn about Prince Chu's love story.

303
00:18:49,119 --> 00:18:50,240
I ran into Liu Heng,

304
00:18:50,240 --> 00:18:51,640
and he brought me here.

305
00:18:52,680 --> 00:18:53,799
Liu Heng,

306
00:18:53,799 --> 00:18:54,960
since when are you so kind?

307
00:18:57,039 --> 00:19:00,039
Well, you don't want Prince Chu to be Emperor either.

308
00:19:00,519 --> 00:19:02,359
So for now, we're on the same side.

309
00:19:03,319 --> 00:19:04,160
Besides,

310
00:19:04,160 --> 00:19:06,119
we're both Liu family brothers, after all.

311
00:19:06,519 --> 00:19:08,039
How could I let outsiders bully you?

312
00:19:08,160 --> 00:19:09,279
That sounds nice and all,

313
00:19:09,279 --> 00:19:10,160
but there are so many guards out there.

314
00:19:10,160 --> 00:19:11,279
How are you getting us out?

315
00:19:12,519 --> 00:19:13,759
Those guards?

316
00:19:14,079 --> 00:19:15,960
I bought them off with a few coins.

317
00:19:16,359 --> 00:19:17,440
That's so strange.

318
00:19:17,480 --> 00:19:18,119
Lady Hero,

319
00:19:18,119 --> 00:19:20,759
you hurt all my brothers just for this?

320
00:19:21,079 --> 00:19:22,039
You should've said so sooner.

321
00:19:22,039 --> 00:19:23,519
I'd have just given it to you.

322
00:19:24,920 --> 00:19:25,799
Wait, didn't you say

323
00:19:25,799 --> 00:19:27,440
this thing was really precious?

324
00:19:27,480 --> 00:19:28,200
Oh, please.

325
00:19:28,200 --> 00:19:30,920
It's only rare down the mountain.

326
00:19:31,319 --> 00:19:32,160
What do you mean?

327
00:19:33,279 --> 00:19:35,119
We spread that rumor ourselves.

328
00:19:35,119 --> 00:19:35,759
Come on.

329
00:19:36,279 --> 00:19:38,079
Rarity makes things valuable.

330
00:19:38,079 --> 00:19:38,640
Right?

331
00:19:38,960 --> 00:19:41,039
That's how you sell it for a high price.

332
00:19:41,039 --> 00:19:41,839
Hunger marketing.

333
00:19:42,480 --> 00:19:43,319
You get it, right?

334
00:19:54,759 --> 00:19:55,559
Let's go.

335
00:19:56,640 --> 00:19:58,559
You'll have three thousand beauties in your harem.

336
00:19:58,839 --> 00:20:00,480
More than you could ever pick from.

337
00:20:01,240 --> 00:20:04,039
You'll forget this Yuji in no time.

338
00:20:06,039 --> 00:20:07,960
Mother, the Emperor never loved you.

339
00:20:08,720 --> 00:20:09,880
Suffering nothing but neglect.

340
00:20:10,880 --> 00:20:12,839
How could you understand my feelings for Yu?

341
00:20:12,839 --> 00:20:13,640
How dare you!

342
00:20:14,039 --> 00:20:15,680
You actually speak to me like this?

343
00:20:16,640 --> 00:20:18,640
Now that Xiao Yu is gone,

344
00:20:19,640 --> 00:20:21,480
what wouldn't I dare to say?

345
00:20:23,160 --> 00:20:24,640
You want me to be Emperor?

346
00:20:24,839 --> 00:20:26,440
Fine, I'll be Emperor.

347
00:20:27,240 --> 00:20:29,319
From now on, you'll be the Empress Dowager.

348
00:20:30,279 --> 00:20:33,160
Whatever you tell me to do, I'll do.

349
00:20:34,640 --> 00:20:35,480
You...

350
00:20:36,680 --> 00:20:38,640
As your mother, I only think of you.

351
00:20:39,119 --> 00:20:40,640
And this is what you think of me?

352
00:20:40,640 --> 00:20:42,319
Whether Mother truly thought of your child,

353
00:20:43,039 --> 00:20:44,839
you know best in your own heart.

354
00:20:47,079 --> 00:20:47,880
Fine.

355
00:20:48,559 --> 00:20:49,640
If that's the case,

356
00:20:50,480 --> 00:20:52,559
I'll order this manor burned down.

357
00:20:53,440 --> 00:20:54,640
And those locked inside...

358
00:20:54,960 --> 00:20:56,440
not one is allowed to escape.

359
00:20:56,680 --> 00:20:57,480
Hey, Prince!

360
00:20:58,039 --> 00:20:59,759
We finally got out!

361
00:21:00,960 --> 00:21:01,759
Xiao Yu!

362
00:21:02,279 --> 00:21:02,680
My Prince.

363
00:21:02,680 --> 00:21:03,960
Xiao Yu, you're alive!

364
00:21:04,519 --> 00:21:05,759
Not for much longer, I'm afraid.

365
00:21:06,240 --> 00:21:07,039
Xiao Yu,

366
00:21:07,920 --> 00:21:08,920
behind your back,

367
00:21:10,039 --> 00:21:11,960
I tricked Mother out of a lot of money.

368
00:21:13,480 --> 00:21:14,359
That money...

369
00:21:15,079 --> 00:21:16,559
Qi Zhi will tell you where it is.

370
00:21:17,240 --> 00:21:18,319
Take that money,

371
00:21:19,319 --> 00:21:20,839
and you can run far away.

372
00:21:21,880 --> 00:21:22,839
Xiao Yu.

373
00:21:23,400 --> 00:21:24,640
Let's leave together.

374
00:21:25,039 --> 00:21:26,880
Life or death no longer matters.

375
00:21:27,759 --> 00:21:28,920
However much time we have,

376
00:21:29,319 --> 00:21:30,839
we'll spend it together.

377
00:21:37,640 --> 00:21:38,440
Mother.

378
00:21:39,240 --> 00:21:40,160
Your child is unfilial.

379
00:21:40,640 --> 00:21:41,839
This Emperor business,

380
00:21:41,839 --> 00:21:43,519
let someone else take it.

381
00:21:44,880 --> 00:21:47,279
You could just run away with Yuji.

382
00:21:47,880 --> 00:21:50,359
But the Special Envoy and Crown Prince,

383
00:21:50,359 --> 00:21:51,640
will you just abandon them?

384
00:22:00,119 --> 00:22:01,880
No one knows a son like his mother.

385
00:22:03,039 --> 00:22:03,960
My son...

386
00:22:04,680 --> 00:22:06,880
you're a man of loyalty and honor.

387
00:22:07,880 --> 00:22:09,880
You would never abandon them.

388
00:22:12,480 --> 00:22:14,319
One day, you'll understand.

389
00:22:15,279 --> 00:22:18,240
Only I have your best interests at heart.

390
00:22:18,759 --> 00:22:19,480
My Prince!

391
00:22:19,480 --> 00:22:20,480
Don't worry about us!

392
00:22:20,640 --> 00:22:21,880
Hurry, take Yuji and go!

393
00:22:22,119 --> 00:22:23,559
It's just itching, isn't it?

394
00:22:23,559 --> 00:22:24,319
Just scratch it.

395
00:22:24,880 --> 00:22:25,720
This poison,

396
00:22:25,720 --> 00:22:27,160
only I can cure it.

397
00:22:28,440 --> 00:22:29,640
If you just walk away,

398
00:22:29,920 --> 00:22:31,720
you'll have killed them both yourself.

399
00:22:32,079 --> 00:22:33,039
Wonderful!

400
00:22:33,039 --> 00:22:33,440
Qi Zhi,

401
00:22:33,640 --> 00:22:34,359
you don't have to die!

402
00:22:34,359 --> 00:22:35,519
Where have you been these past two days?

403
00:22:35,920 --> 00:22:36,720
I...

404
00:22:37,640 --> 00:22:38,319
The antidote!

405
00:22:38,319 --> 00:22:39,119
Ah!

406
00:22:41,160 --> 00:22:42,799
The medicine's here.

407
00:22:42,799 --> 00:22:43,640
Come, come.

408
00:22:44,759 --> 00:22:45,559
Careful, it's hot.

409
00:22:47,680 --> 00:22:48,480
Slowly.

410
00:22:50,480 --> 00:22:51,279
So bitter!

411
00:22:54,319 --> 00:22:55,119
Hey,

412
00:22:55,119 --> 00:22:55,920
it's gone!

413
00:22:56,720 --> 00:22:57,680
The itching stopped!

414
00:22:57,680 --> 00:22:58,319
That fast?

415
00:22:59,279 --> 00:23:00,279
Are you feeling better?

416
00:23:07,480 --> 00:23:08,279
Xiao Yu.

417
00:23:08,559 --> 00:23:09,359
My Prince.

418
00:23:09,839 --> 00:23:10,559
It's amazing!

419
00:23:12,079 --> 00:23:13,640
We can be together forever now!

420
00:23:20,759 --> 00:23:22,359
What are you doing?

421
00:23:35,039 --> 00:23:36,240
Is it really that bitter?

422
00:23:48,640 --> 00:23:49,720
Come on, come on, bottoms up!

423
00:23:49,720 --> 00:23:50,720
It's bitter and you still chug it?

424
00:23:52,079 --> 00:23:53,720
Why is he the only one not cured?

425
00:23:55,279 --> 00:23:57,640
Hurry, save him!

426
00:23:58,880 --> 00:24:00,119
I already told him.

427
00:24:01,039 --> 00:24:02,319
His condition, I can't cure it.

428
00:24:10,920 --> 00:24:12,160
This is just too incredible!

429
00:24:12,279 --> 00:24:13,240
It's downright shocking!

430
00:24:14,960 --> 00:24:16,720
Works even better than Tiger Balm!

431
00:24:21,480 --> 00:24:23,640
Just don't hit him from now on, that's all.

432
00:24:39,480 --> 00:24:40,640
What's wrong with you?

433
00:24:40,880 --> 00:24:42,119
What are you so sad about?

434
00:24:44,079 --> 00:24:45,720
I'm not sad at all.

435
00:24:46,519 --> 00:24:47,960
It's perfect if you die.

436
00:24:48,359 --> 00:24:49,559
From now on,

437
00:24:49,559 --> 00:24:52,480
I won't have to protect you anymore.

438
00:24:53,079 --> 00:24:54,240
And I can

439
00:24:54,240 --> 00:24:58,200
marry whoever I want.

440
00:24:58,480 --> 00:25:01,160
You don't care about me anyway.

441
00:25:01,400 --> 00:25:02,039
I know.

442
00:25:03,839 --> 00:25:04,759
Wait,

443
00:25:04,759 --> 00:25:07,519
why would I be dying?

444
00:25:08,920 --> 00:25:09,720
Oh.

445
00:25:09,720 --> 00:25:11,640
You mean these red spots?

446
00:25:11,960 --> 00:25:12,839
No, no.

447
00:25:12,839 --> 00:25:14,039
These aren't from any illness.

448
00:25:14,720 --> 00:25:15,519
Yeah.

449
00:25:15,880 --> 00:25:18,240
These are from you hitting me.

450
00:25:23,839 --> 00:25:24,640
Oh.

451
00:25:25,680 --> 00:25:28,440
Now I know why you've been like this.

452
00:25:30,119 --> 00:25:31,240
I'm sorry I put you through this.

453
00:25:35,720 --> 00:25:37,640
If you ever scare me like that again,

454
00:25:37,880 --> 00:25:39,319
I'll beat you so your mom won't know you.

455
00:25:40,039 --> 00:25:40,839
Hey.

456
00:25:46,759 --> 00:25:47,559
Sigh.

457
00:25:48,839 --> 00:25:50,079
Qi Zhi was in a daze.

458
00:25:50,480 --> 00:25:51,640
He finally realized

459
00:25:51,640 --> 00:25:53,519
that Ouyang Yan cared about him this much.

460
00:25:54,720 --> 00:25:56,279
He couldn't help but ask himself,

461
00:25:56,720 --> 00:25:58,839
with such a wonderful girl before him,

462
00:25:59,079 --> 00:26:01,880
could he just watch her marry another?

463
00:26:02,640 --> 00:26:03,480
Sigh.

464
00:26:03,960 --> 00:26:05,279
The ending of this story

465
00:26:05,279 --> 00:26:07,680
is one he must write himself.

466
00:26:12,480 --> 00:26:14,720
Stop adding random inner monologues!

467
00:26:21,640 --> 00:26:22,079
Hey.

468
00:26:22,519 --> 00:26:24,359
Walking so fast, what are you thinking about?

469
00:26:25,480 --> 00:26:26,079
Huh?

470
00:26:26,079 --> 00:26:27,200
Get away from me!

471
00:26:27,200 --> 00:26:29,039
Don't pass your fatal illness to me.

472
00:26:29,279 --> 00:26:30,039
Hey!

473
00:26:31,039 --> 00:26:33,039
Didn't I say it's from you hitting me?
